# Normalize line endings: text files are stored as LF in the repo and checked
# out as LF everywhere. This repo is developed on Windows (core.autocrlf=true)
# but its files are LF; without this, editors/tools that rewrite a file with
# CRLF produce whole-file diffs. Declaring the intent here makes it deterministic
# regardless of each contributor's git config.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never touch their bytes.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
